/***
 * class Pig
 * a Pig Latin translator
 * ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ SKELETON ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 *           9
 *     ,--.-'-,--.
 *     \  /-~-\  /
 *    / )' a a `( \
 *   ( (  ,---.  ) )
 *    \ `(_o_o_)' /
 *     \   `-'   /
 *      | |---| |
 *      [_]   [_]
 *      PROTIP: Make this class compilable first,
 *      then develop and test one method at a time.
 *      NEVER STRAY TOO FAR FROM COMPILABILITY/RUNNABILITY!
 ***/
